# Backstage Operational Dashboards Configuration

Backstage provides operational dashboards for monitoring system health, tracking dependencies, and managing the service landscape.

---

## Dashboard Types & Configuration

### System Overview Dashboard

Provides a high-level view of all services, their status, and health.

```json
{
  "id": "system-overview",
  "title": "System Overview",
  "description": "Health and status of all services in Lux-Auto",
  "type": "overview",
  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "service-status",
      "title": "Service Status",
      "type": "service-grid",
      "components": [
        {
          "service": "lux-fastapi-backend",
          "displayName": "FastAPI Backend",
          "healthCheck": "https://lux.kushnir.cloud/health",
          "metrics": ["uptime", "response_time", "error_rate"]
        },
        {
          "service": "lux-appsmith-portal",
          "displayName": "Appsmith Portal",
          "healthCheck": "https://appsmith.lux.kushnir.cloud/api/v1/health",
          "metrics": ["uptime", "user_sessions"]
        },
        {
          "service": "lux-backstage-catalog",
          "displayName": "Backstage Catalog",
          "healthCheck": "https://backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/api/health",
          "metrics": ["uptime", "entity_count"]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "infrastructure",
      "title": "Infrastructure",
      "type": "resource-status",
      "resources": [
        {
          "name": "PostgreSQL",
          "type": "database",
          "status": "GET /api/v2/admin/health/postgres",
          "metrics": ["connections", "disk_usage", "query_time"]
        },
        {
          "name": "Redis",
          "type": "cache",
          "status": "GET /api/v2/admin/health/redis",
          "metrics": ["memory_usage", "hit_rate", "evictions"]
        },
        {
          "name": "Docker Containers",
          "type": "containers",
          "metrics": ["cpu_usage", "memory_usage", "restart_count"]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "recent-deployments",
      "title": "Recent Deployments",
      "type": "deployment-timeline",
      "limit": 10,
      "showBy": ["timestamp", "service", "version", "status"]
    }
  ]
}
```

