## Dashboard Integration

### Grafana Integration

Connect to Grafana dashboards from Backstage:

```yaml
apiVersion: backstage.io/v1alpha1
kind: Dashboard
metadata:
  name: lux-auto-grafana
  title: Grafana Integration
spec:
  provider: grafana
  url: https://lux.kushnir.cloud/grafana
  dashboards:
    - id: api-health
      title: API Health
      description: Real-time API performance metrics
      tags: [api, performance]
    - id: database-health
      title: Database Health
      description: PostgreSQL metrics and health
      tags: [database, infrastructure]
    - id: resource-utilization
      title: Resource Utilization
      description: CPU, memory, disk usage
      tags: [infrastructure, resources]
```

### PagerDuty Integration

Link incidents and on-call schedules:

```yaml
apiVersion: backstage.io/v1alpha1
kind: OnCall
metadata:
  name: lux-auto-oncall
  title: On-Call Schedule
spec:
  provider: pagerduty
  schedules:
    - id: backend-oncall
      service: lux-fastapi-backend
      escalationPolicy: backend-escalation
    - id: devops-oncall
      service: infrastructure
      escalationPolicy: devops-escalation
```

### Datadog Integration

Monitor real-time metrics:

```yaml
apiVersion: backstage.io/v1alpha1
kind: Monitoring
metadata:
  name: lux-auto-datadog
  title: Datadog Monitoring
spec:
  provider: datadog
  organizations:
    - name: Lux-Auto
      apiKey: ${DATADOG_API_KEY}
      metrics:
        - api_response_time
        - error_rate
        - db_query_time
        - cache_hit_rate
```

