## Setup Instructions

### 1. Register Dashboard Entities

```bash
# Register all dashboards in Backstage
curl -X POST \
  https://backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/api/catalog/entities \
  -H "Content-Type: application/yaml" \
  -d @dashboards/system-overview.yaml

curl -X POST \
  https://backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/api/catalog/entities \
  -H "Content-Type: application/yaml" \
  -d @dashboards/dependency-graph.yaml
```

### 2. Configure Data Sources

1. Go to Backstage → **Settings**
2. Configure API endpoints for each data source
3. Test connections
4. Save configurations

### 3. Enable Real-Time Updates

```yaml
# Enable WebSocket for real-time updates
ws:
  enabled: true
  url: wss://backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/api/ws
  reconnect:
    maxAttempts: 5
    delayMs: 1000
```

### 4. Set Up Notifications

Configure alerts to notify teams of critical issues:

```yaml
notifications:
  slack:
    webhookUrl: ${SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL}
    channels:
      - incidents
      - alerts
  email:
    enabled: true
    recipients:
      - ops@lux-auto.com
```

