## Accessing Dashboards

1. **System Overview**: `backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/dashboards/system-overview`
2. **Dependency Graph**: `backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/dashboards/dependency-graph`
3. **API Health**: `backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/dashboards/api-health`
4. **Resource Monitoring**: `backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/dashboards/resource-monitoring`
5. **Audit & Compliance**: `backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/dashboards/audit-compliance`
6. **Team & Ownership**: `backstage.lux.kushnir.cloud/dashboards/team-ownership`

